org.incava.ijdk.lang

Class Obj<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.incava.ijdk.lang.Obj<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of object being wrapped
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bool
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Int, Str

    public class Obj<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Bool
    Extension to the Object class, wrapping a JDK Object with additional methods. The referenced object can be null. Also has "boolean-ness" of an object, which can be true, false, or empty.
